						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the entrance of the village.</p>						

						<p>DĒVARĀYA VOḌAYALU.</p>						

						<p>1386 A.D.</p>						

						<p>It is dated Śaka 1308, Kshaya, Vaiśākha śu. 11, Thursday corresponding to 1386 A.D. April 11, Wednesday, f.d.t. °04.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Records the construction of tank on the southern side by Yirugama reḍimāramareḍi. It further states that gift of a royal land <hi rend="italic">(prabhu-mānyam)</hi> measuring one <hi rend="italic">puṭṭi,</hi> probably for irrigation under this tank and also mention the remission of one <hi rend="italic">iddumu</hi> as <hi rend="italic">Dasavanda</hi> tax.</p>						

						</summary>
